title: Mango
lyrics: Tone jeokdanghi ne yeope dugie ...heumi eopsdan iyuro ...neon nareul gollanaesseo ne kkadaron ipmase majchwoseo ...budeureopge noga jul ...neon geureon geol wonhaesseo naegeseo gajiryeoneun ge naui mami anin ge da neukkyeojineunde I feel you ...nega nareul wonhaneun iyuga kkeopjilppunin georamyeon ....I can make you I can make you man Man go Man go sigannangbi malgo sigannangbi malgo Man go Man go geoseulliji malgo geoseulliji malgo naega hyanggiropgo tto mulleo boyeodo sigo tdeolpeun Mango, simji godeun Mango naega chakhae boigo yakhae boyeodo nan teukbyeolhan Mango. I can make you man man go deol igeun nae mameul bogodo ...neon seonggeuphi gureossji nal magu jjilleodaessji neo ttaeme nae sogi sseokneun geon yongnap moshaji I don’t like it seoltangeul bareun geu mareun nareul ganjireophyeodo kkumyeojin georamyeon nan silhgu ...yeogiga pojangdoen ...ne mamui yutonggihaniramyeon I can make you I I can make you man Man go Man go sigannangbi malgo sigannangbi malgo Man go Man go geoseulliji malgo geoseulliji malgo naega hyanggiropgo tto mulleo boyeodo sigo tdeolpeun Mango simji godeun Mango naega chakhae boigo yakhae boyeodo nan teukbyeolhan Mango geubi dareun Mango nal jjilleoboneun geora myeon take your hands off me nal sideulge haryeogo handamyeon then I’ll just walk away money money neon tto mwoni jeoryeomhan taedoe nan deo hwanaji honey honey neon dareuni I can make you man Man go Man go sigannangbi malgo sigannangbi malgo Man go Man go geoseulliji malgo geoseulliji malgo nan teukbyeolhan Mango
